     C     *ENTRY        PLIST

      ** Inputs
      ** Return Code

     C                   PARM                    RetCodeIn
     C                   PARM                    PFscd

      ** Error fields/message IDs/message data (arrays) from/to caller

     C                   PARM                    FldNamXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgIDXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgDtaXAr

      ** Warning fields/message IDs/message data (arrays) from/to
      ** caller

     C                   PARM                    WFldNmXAr
     C                   PARM                    WMsgIDXAr
     C                   PARM                    WMsgDtXAr
     C                   PARM                    DDTFscdOk         1                      LUC139

